name: Lady in Blue Chapeau Print
description:
Presented is a mysterious lady, whom you don't know, but very much want to meet.

Size: 8"x10"
  
Bigger sizes available! See below.

Originally painted on canvas with acrylic and signed by the artist.

Photographed to represent the true colors, but they may vary depending on your monitor.

Format Options:
8”x10” Print $26
11”x14” Print $30
16”x20” Print $39
20”x30” Print $46

Tax: Included.

Shipping Everywhere: Free.  Allow 3-10 business days US.  6-14 business days international.

TO ORDER:
If you just want the $26 8”x10” Print as listed with the semi-gloss paper then click “Add to Cart”.

TO CUSTOM ORDER:
Choose your size from the drop down menu, and click "Add to Cart".  I will then send an invoice to your e-mail via PayPal for the difference.

EX. You want the $30 11"x14".
1. Choose "11"x14" Print $30", "Add to Cart" and pay $26.
2. I will then send an invoice to you for $4.

NOTE: Orders will not be processed until payment is received.
